Atin pang adwang karagdagang layout a tambing nang misamasan (pre-defined)
*<code><nowiki>{{POTD/{{#time:Y-m-d}}|column}}</nowiki></code>: Keti, mitutumpak la reng larawan ampong sulat, at alang gulis (border). Magagamit ya iti kareng mapilan a [[Wikipedia:Main Page alternatives|Main Page alternatives]] at bage ya murin kareng user page.
*<code><nowiki>{{POTD/{{#time:Y-m-d}}|row}}</nowiki></code>: Keti, makalulan la king (keraklan) metung a dane ning table (table row). Ini ing bersion a magagamit king [[Pun Bulung]].
Malyari ya muring permanenting ibili ing Larawan ning Aldo para king metung a mepiling aldo. Idagdag me mu ing particular a bilang (value) ketang petsang buri mu. Alimbawa, ing Larawan ning Aldo ngeni anti ya kaniti
<code>{{tlp|POTD/{{CURRENTYEAR}}-{{CURRENTMONTH}}-{{CURRENTDAY2}}|image}}</code>. Malyari mu la muring gamitan deng balangkas (parameter) ning petsa kareng aliwang apusan o template. Nung buri mo retang sadya nang megawa, agamit mu la rin deng date parameter kareta, anti kaniti: 
<code><nowiki>{{</nowiki>[[Template:Pic of the day|Pic of the day]]|date={{CURRENTYEAR}}-{{CURRENTMONTH}}-{{CURRENTDAY2}}}}</code> o
<code><nowiki>{{</nowiki>[[Template:POTD|POTD]]|date={{CURRENTYEAR}}-{{CURRENTMONTH}}-{{CURRENTDAY2}}}}</code>. Pasibayu, 
'''Gumana ya mu ing sistemang iti kareng Larawan ning Aldo manibat Enero 1, 2007.'''

===Deng minunang larawan ning aldo===
Nung buri meng permanenting iyabe ing metung a Larawan ning Aldo a mepili king pilatan ning Noviembre 1, 2004 at Diciembre 31, 2006, gamitan me ing makatuki:
<code><nowiki>{{Wikipedia:Picture of the day/[month] [day], [year]}}</nowiki></code> o <code><nowiki>{{Wikipedia:POTD/[month] [day], [year]}}</nowiki></code>. Alimbawa, <code><nowiki>{{Wikipedia:Picture of the day/December 31, 2006}}</nowiki></code>.

Den namang Larawan ning Aldong mepili manibat ketang Mayo 2004 anggang Octubre 2004, malyari la mung puntalan kapamilatan da reng archivo para king balang bulan (month-at-a-time), at malyari lang ibili kareng user pages nung gamitan ya ing [[Help:Images and other uploaded files|standard image syntax]].

